{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_35","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed, but the preserved work branch appears to contain a working fix: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-7340-fails-native-image-run-jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api-3.0.0-80ceab3a\n\nThe most likely failing stage was post-fix workflow finalization/orchestration, not the native-image run itself. In `human-intervention-logs/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api:3.0.0/metadata-fix/codex.log`, the preserved run adds the missing JSTL resource/service metadata and a root-bundle fallback test, then finishes with `BUILD SUCCESSFUL`; the native run reports 12/12 tests successful. The generated `stats/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api/3.0.0/stats.json` also shows resource dynamic-access coverage at 2/2 (1.0). In `human-intervention-logs/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api:3.0.0/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`, URL maintenance also completes successfully after replacing the stale `test-code-url`, with concrete evidence that `https://download.eclipse.org/jakartaee/tags/3.0/jakarta-tags-tck-3.0.2.zip` returned 404.\n\nThe preserved branch already contains changes to `metadata/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api/3.0.0/reachability-metadata.json`, `tests/src/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api/3.0.0/src/test/java/jakarta_servlet_jsp_jstl/jakarta_servlet_jsp_jstl_api/Jakarta_servlet_jsp_jstl_apiTest.java`, and `metadata/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api/index.json`.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `human-intervention-logs/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api:3.0.0/metadata-fix/codex.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api:3.0.0/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`\n- `tests/src/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api/3.0.0/test-results-native/test/TEST-junit-jupiter.xml`\n- `stats/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl/jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api/3.0.0/stats.json`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Review and manually carry over the preserved branch changes into a PR if they look correct.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api:3.0.0` and `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl:jakarta.servlet.jsp.jstl-api:3.0.0`.\n3. Inspect the workflow finalization/publication step, because both preserved substeps succeeded while the overall run still ended as `job_failed`."}}
